{"word":"H7251 - רָבַע - râbaʻ - raw-bah' - Square","slug":"H7251","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָבַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Square"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D1;&#x05E2; - ra&#x0302;ba&#x201B;</b> - <i>raw-bah'</i><p/>A primitive root (rather identical with <a href=\"#/H7250\">H7250</a> through the idea of <i>sprawling</i> at all fours (or possibly the reverse is the order of derivation); compare <a href=\"#/H702\">H702</a>); properly to <i>be four</i> (sided); used only as denominative of <a href=\"#/H7253\">H7253</a>; to <i>be quadrate: - </i>(four-) square (-d)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H702\">H702</a>, <a href=\"#/H705\">H705</a>, <a href=\"#/H706\">H706</a>, <a href=\"#/H7243\">H7243</a>, <a href=\"#/H7253\">H7253</a>, <a href=\"#/H7255\">H7255</a>, <a href=\"#/H7256\">H7256</a>"}]}